title: Silent Wedding (2008)
description:
Silent Wedding (2008) 

In a small isolated village, in 1953, a wedding is interrupted by the news about the death of Stalin. Because any public celebration is forbidden, they decide to turn the happy event into a silent wedding. Director: Horatiu Malaele.  Stars: Meda Andreea Victor, Alexandru Potocean, Valentin Teodosiu.

From Romania, in Romanian

Subtitles by SBS AU TV
